snippet.title: *New* Dokimon + MonMae Trailer - Monster Tamer Direct 2024
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Long time no chat~ Today I'm sharing the video we entered in Gym Leader Ed's Monster Taming Direct for 2024. Overall really happy to have been able to participate in the direct and see what's new with everyone else in the monster taming community~

Definitely check out Ed's YouTube channel if you wanna see the other games that appeared there:  @GymLeaderEd  

And this video wouldn't have been possible without the great help of my good friend Tosh! He is our voice over and video editor and you can follow him and his projects on X / Twitter at the following link:
https://x.com/gamedevtosh

Cheers!


Brought to you by: Yanako RPGs LLC
https://www.yanakorpgs.com

Learn more about us and our games on itch.io!
https://yanako-rpgs.itch.io/
